div.p:
Ỽrth ỿ gair Maeth ỿ mae i chỽidhealh ỿ neb oedh ỿn peri
maeth. Mỿnychiaỽn ỿr arbherir ỿ droelh hon ỿn ganmoladỽy;
oblegyd ei bod ỿn nerthau‘r araith ỿn rỿmmys.

Ỿr vn modh ỿ rhaid barnu, pan dhigỽydho cỿmhariat lheiadog.
Megys pann dhỿỽedỽn bhod rhyỽ beth ỿn lhai no‘r gỽreinyn;
neu daccỽ dhyn cỿn lheied a‘m dỽrn.

Ỿ barnỽr alỿgra gỿbhraith; ỿ duỽinỽr a athraỽo grỽydrdhyſc;
ỿ phỿſỿgỽr a gam-bhedheginiaetha; bo idhynt draethirion,
ac enioes bherr ar ỿ dhaiar.

Dyn yỽ eghraph o ỽendid; delỽ anỽadalỽch; cribdhail amſer;
alhtud trueni; lheſtr aighc annigonadỽy; a chaſtelh adbhail
diſỿmmỽth.
